{"tid":1609671,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[緊急新戰線] 全民GIF圖賀佢老母","createTime":"2019-10-01T15:09:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T02:33:45.000Z","uid":91558,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"f3188e1cdbbd393ed001eeb3280f09ad135c777f","tid":1609671,"uid":91558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T15:09:14.000Z","msg":"地獄鬼國成立70周年，愛國連登仔點少得係facebook同佢地贈興？<br />\n但係用文字真係好難表達個種感情，又唔比人upload圖<br />\n咁叫人點愛國呀？？<br />\n<br />\n不過，小妹發現原來將Twitter，Facebook Video download落黎<br />\n用<a href=\"https://tenor.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftenor.com&d=JxnAwUrH%2B1qYxVTFfur%2BVmmu51%2BDyw7Majob2ybULac%3D&h=c2e0bd92\" target=\"_blank\">https://tenor.com</a>轉成GIF檔，唔駛登入就放得上<a href=\"http://giphy.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgiphy.com&d=JxnAwUrH%2B1qYxVTFfur%2BVmmu51%2BDyw7Majob2ybULac%3D&h=29bfddbd\" target=\"_blank\">giphy.com</a><br />\n將條link放落留言到，就會出到GIF圖架啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n時間關係，已經整左個GIF list同post list比大家輕鬆賀佢老母啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1aRXq9dedJKs8TzQTipIouCkvJZnAcXnj-vYJ-dscfnA/edit?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fdocument%2Fd%2F1aRXq9dedJKs8TzQTipIouCkvJZnAcXnj-vYJ-dscfnA%2Fedit%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=JxnAwUrH%2B1qYxVTFfur%2BVmmu51%2BDyw7Majob2ybULac%3D&h=fa85b7df\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/document/d/1aRXq9dedJKs8TzQTipIouCkvJZnAcXnj-vYJ-dscfnA/edit?usp=sharing</a><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">十月一仲剩番一個鐘，大家快D手啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kCGSMPC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkCGSMPC.jpg&h=8dbf104b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n恐怖組織Page都放到圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n攻擊目標：<br />\n恐怖分子<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/HongKongPoliceForce/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHongKongPoliceForce%2F&d=JxnAwUrH%2B1qYxVTFfur%2BVmmu51%2BDyw7Majob2ybULac%3D&h=eb990620\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/HongKongPoliceForce/</a><br />\n民建聯 <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1552838541623337/posts/2393896397517543?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1552838541623337%2Fposts%2F2393896397517543%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=JxnAwUrH%2B1qYxVTFfur%2BVmmu51%2BDyw7Majob2ybULac%3D&h=f76c14a9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1552838541623337/posts/2393896397517543?sfns=mo</a><br />\nCCTV<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cctvcom/videos/2043163319117666/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcctvcom%2Fvideos%2F2043163319117666%2F&d=JxnAwUrH%2B1qYxVTFfur%2BVmmu51%2BDyw7Majob2ybULac%3D&h=52e70d6f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/cctvcom/videos/2043163319117666/</a>"},{"pid":"a6dcb16dc5677c9a4f40ebbf6a90304324d230fb","tid":1609671,"uid":91558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T15:09:38.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"000e93bf2a23e75df48a1ea4b9d7393a68f113cd","tid":1609671,"uid":91558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T15:09:54.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"4c6163daff6b72f8a5e26c7ecb76b3edebd73668","tid":1609671,"uid":91558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T15:10:04.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"829f5c63bf7e88d76bd3d8ca521ea43f7757b282","tid":1609671,"uid":91558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T15:10:41.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"2057511447a97e190a230f6a23dfe4565f6fb1e3","tid":1609671,"uid":260830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cit